    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, and the subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. While showing honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a recently serviced VANOS system and documented valve adjustment. A purist\u2019s spec focused on visceral feedback and longitudinal performance.",
